## BirthdayDrop — Environment Variables
## Copy this to .env and fill in your values.
## NEVER commit your real .env to version control!

## ── MongoDB Atlas (REQUIRED for Vercel) ──────────────────────
## Get your connection string from https://cloud.mongodb.com
## Replace <user>, <password>, and <cluster> with your own values.
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://<user>:<password>@<cluster>.mongodb.net/birthdaydrop?retryWrites=true&w=majority

## ── Local MongoDB (for local dev only) ───────────────────────
## MONGO_URI=mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/birthdaydrop

## ── Express Server (local dev only, not used by Vercel) ──────
PORT=5000
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173
